<normalizedToken id="18D16227CF647CAE3EAD37E502E6E585" originalValue="A–D">A-D</normalizedToken>
, 7
<normalizedToken id="E7C1454BBF6913796A0270289AF196D1" originalValue="A–D">A-D</normalizedToken>
, 6E, 8F).
</paragraph>
